  "title": "Operations Driver",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>To deliver and pick up customer cars</li>\n  <li>To deliver and pick up car parts/accessories or documents</li>\n  <li>Assist with shiftingA  cars in the workshop</li>\n  <li>Ability to multitask</li>\n  <li>Detail-oriented; able to work in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills and good interaction with people</li>\n  <li>Team player with a positive attitude</li>\n  <li>Class 3 license requires at least 2 years of driving experience</li>\n  <li>Safety driver and drive with care</li>\n  <li>Able to start work on short notice</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc jobs, if any</li>\n  <li>Singaporean citizenship or permanent resident</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Workplace in Sin Ming Area (near Bishan)</p>\n<p>To apply for this job, please contact 96788908</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>交付和提取客户汽车</li>\n  <li>交付和领取汽车零件/配件或文件</li>\n  <li>协助车厂换车</li>\n  <li>多任务处理能力</li>\n  <li>注重细节；能够在快节奏的环境中工作</li>\n  <li>良好的沟通能力和与人良好的互动</li>\n  <li>具有积极态度的团队合作者</li>\n  <li>3 级驾照需要至少 2 年驾驶经验</li>\n  <li>安全驾驶，小心驾驶</li>\n  <li>能够在短时间内开始工作</li>\n  <li>其他临时工作（如果有）</li>\n  <li>仅限新加坡和新加坡永久居民申请人</li>\n</ul>\n<p>新民区工作地点 (靠近劈山区）</p>\n<p>申请此职位请联系96788908</p>",
